1
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:30,000
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:33,850
[Episode 34]

3
00:01:34,020 --> 00:01:36,289
[Marquis of Zhongyong's Mansion]

4
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:36,150
Father, Mother.

5
00:01:36,150 --> 00:01:37,400
Yu is back.

6
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,710
Yu. My dear Yu.

7
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:39,789
-Mother.
-You're finally back.

8
00:01:39,789 --> 00:01:41,560
It was with great difficulty that
I gained the Empress Dowager's pity

9
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,840
and was granted the chance
to leave the palace,

10
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,759
so I cannot stay for long.

11
00:01:43,759 --> 00:01:45,740
I have important matters
to discuss with Father.

12
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:47,830
Mother, please return to your room
and rest.

13
00:01:47,830 --> 00:01:49,180
I want to stay with you, Yu.

14
00:01:49,180 --> 00:01:50,020
Yan,

15
00:01:50,050 --> 00:01:51,450
escort your mother back.

16
00:01:52,030 --> 00:01:53,490
I'll wait for you outside.

17
00:01:53,910 --> 00:01:54,580
Mother.

18
00:02:01,890 --> 00:02:04,220
This is a letter from the Empress
to her brother, General Zhao.

19
00:02:04,220 --> 00:02:07,290
Please deliver it to the Northern Army
as soon as possible, Father.

20
00:02:07,290 --> 00:02:08,800
What exactly happened?

21
00:02:09,930 --> 00:02:12,050
The Crown Prince was eager
to defend his mother

22
00:02:12,050 --> 00:02:14,050
and ended up offending His Majesty.

23
00:02:19,250 --> 00:02:20,079
Father.

24
00:02:26,570 --> 00:02:27,380
Okay.

25
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:30,740
I'll send your brother
to deliver it immediately.

26
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:31,670
The Empress said

27
00:02:31,980 --> 00:02:33,990
we must first ensure
the Crown Prince's safety

28
00:02:33,990 --> 00:02:35,710
before planning our next move.

29
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:37,370
I understand what's at stake.

30
00:02:38,060 --> 00:02:39,720
I'll return to the palace now.

31
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:42,270
Yu.

32
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:47,150
Must you really
accompany the Crown Prince

33
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:50,010
during his confinement
in the Imperial Clan Court?

34
00:02:51,740 --> 00:02:52,870
Wherever he is,

35
00:02:53,230 --> 00:02:54,460
that's where I'll be.

36
00:02:57,230 --> 00:02:57,900
Alright.

37
00:02:59,060 --> 00:02:59,990
You may leave.

38
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:02,280
Once everything is arranged,

39
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:03,520
I will send someone

40
00:03:03,830 --> 00:03:05,490
to deliver the message to you.

41
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:07,780
I, Yu,

42
00:03:09,580 --> 00:03:11,270
thank you, Father.

43
00:03:24,270 --> 00:03:25,670
Farewell, Your Majesty.

44
00:03:38,990 --> 00:03:39,670
Sui.

45
00:03:40,270 --> 00:03:43,000
Are you still afraid of your father,
His Majesty?

46
00:03:44,270 --> 00:03:45,950
Then can you tell me

47
00:03:45,950 --> 00:03:47,480
what you're worried about?

48
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,640
Father is very angry.

49
00:03:49,990 --> 00:03:52,670
Will Mother and Che die?

50
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:56,040
Here.

51
00:04:01,270 --> 00:04:02,990
Sui, don't worry.

52
00:04:03,270 --> 00:04:06,110
Her Majesty and His Highness
just did something wrong,

53
00:04:06,110 --> 00:04:07,270
and His Majesty only deposed them

54
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:09,870
from the position of Empress
and Crown Prince.

55
00:04:10,970 --> 00:04:13,110
If only people didn't have to die.

56
00:04:13,740 --> 00:04:14,990
Once they die,

57
00:04:14,990 --> 00:04:16,890
they can't speak

58
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:18,620
or move anymore,

59
00:04:19,180 --> 00:04:21,260
just like my mother.

60
00:04:22,470 --> 00:04:24,380
Consort Jin was a fairy from heaven.

61
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:25,350
Now that you've grown up,

62
00:04:25,350 --> 00:04:26,940
of course she had to return.

63
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:29,740
The dead cannot come back to life,

64
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:31,490
nor do they return to heaven.

65
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:34,420
Wan, you don't have to comfort me
with lies.

66
00:04:34,620 --> 00:04:35,740
Sui...

67
00:04:36,740 --> 00:04:37,650
Little Wan'er!

68
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:44,230
Why has Che been confined
in the Imperial Clan Court?

69
00:04:44,230 --> 00:04:45,409
Such a refined person as he is,

70
00:04:45,409 --> 00:04:48,610
how could he have behaved improperly
before His Majesty?

71
00:04:51,140 --> 00:04:53,180
That's not something we should discuss.

72
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:53,990
Right, right.

73
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:55,990
It's none of our business,
so we shouldn't pry.

74
00:04:55,990 --> 00:04:56,820
Sui.

75
00:04:56,820 --> 00:04:58,220
Don't follow my example.

76
00:05:00,380 --> 00:05:02,110
Have you visited the Empress Dowager?

77
00:05:02,110 --> 00:05:03,060
Not yet.

78
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:06,060
Yan asked me to invite you and Chi
to his residence.

79
00:05:06,060 --> 00:05:07,380
He said he needs your help with something.

80
00:05:07,380 --> 00:05:08,380
Both of us?

81
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,380
Not just me for medical treatment?

82
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:11,380
Yan specifically instructed

83
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:13,180
you to bring your coroner's kit.

84
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:17,170
[Prince Xin's Mansion]

85
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:26,530
Your Highness, they're here.

86
00:05:32,909 --> 00:05:33,700
Esteemed couple.

87
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:34,990
Newly wedded as you are,

88
00:05:34,990 --> 00:05:36,110
I apologize for the intrusion.

89
00:05:36,110 --> 00:05:37,370
I truly have no choice.

90
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:38,300
Chi.

91
00:05:38,470 --> 00:05:39,820
You won't blame me, will you?

92
00:05:39,820 --> 00:05:40,940
You jest, Yan.

93
00:05:42,590 --> 00:05:44,430
Has your eyesight improved, Yan?

94
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:45,960
Thanks to Wan's treatment,

95
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:47,870
my vision has indeed improved,

96
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:48,980
though

97
00:05:49,230 --> 00:05:50,680
I can only make out shapes

98
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:51,790
in dim light.

99
00:05:52,300 --> 00:05:54,380
Yan, why did you ask me
to bring my coroner's kit?

100
00:05:54,380 --> 00:05:55,380
If there's any legal matter,

101
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:57,110
it's best to report it
to the authorities first.

102
00:05:57,110 --> 00:05:58,260
It concerns a private matter

103
00:05:58,260 --> 00:06:00,030
from years ago
in Prince Xin's family.

104
00:06:00,030 --> 00:06:01,760
Before the truth is uncovered,

105
00:06:01,990 --> 00:06:03,550
Wan and Chi, I kindly ask you both

106
00:06:03,550 --> 00:06:04,940
to keep this matter discreet.

107
00:06:04,940 --> 00:06:06,070
That's only proper.

108
00:06:26,910 --> 00:06:27,700
Mother.

109
00:06:29,550 --> 00:06:32,020
I've brought Chi and his wife, Wan,

110
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:32,990
to see you.

111
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:36,140
Are these...

112
00:06:37,550 --> 00:06:39,409
The late Princess Xin's remains?

113
00:06:43,740 --> 00:06:44,790
All these years,

114
00:06:45,550 --> 00:06:47,060
I've done everything in my power

115
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:48,950
to preserve Mother's body,

116
00:06:51,110 --> 00:06:52,770
but this is the best I could do.

117
00:06:53,909 --> 00:06:56,909
Yan, do you want me to perform an autopsy
on the late Princess's body?

118
00:06:56,909 --> 00:06:57,740
Why?

119
00:06:58,700 --> 00:06:59,900
Because I want to know

120
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:04,010
what exactly caused Mother's death.

121
00:07:07,330 --> 00:07:08,640
Please help me, Wan.

122
00:07:10,470 --> 00:07:12,130
Yan, there's no need for this.

123
00:07:12,150 --> 00:07:13,680
I will certainly do my best.

124
00:07:14,030 --> 00:07:14,910
It's just

125
00:07:15,470 --> 00:07:17,060
investigating the cause of death

126
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:19,030
will inevitably damage the body.

127
00:07:19,030 --> 00:07:21,290
It would be best for you to stay away,
Yan.

128
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:22,500
It's okay.

129
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:24,800
She's already gone,

130
00:07:25,870 --> 00:07:26,940
and her body

131
00:07:26,940 --> 00:07:28,350
will eventually turn to dust.

132
00:07:28,350 --> 00:07:29,030
The truth

133
00:07:29,820 --> 00:07:31,380
is my only consolation now.

134
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,640
Mother's spirit in heaven

135
00:07:35,380 --> 00:07:37,260
will surely understand my intentions.

136
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:38,430
Besides,

137
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:40,180
Wan, you probably don't know that

138
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:41,670
before my late mother was married,

139
00:07:41,670 --> 00:07:43,060
she also studied with the Medicine King,

140
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:45,300
learning pharmaceutical skills for a year,

141
00:07:45,300 --> 00:07:47,560
making her somewhat his apprentice too.

142
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:49,480
She had long come to terms with

143
00:07:49,620 --> 00:07:50,670
the cycle of life and death,

144
00:07:50,670 --> 00:07:52,670
and surely wouldn't mind
what happens after she died.

145
00:07:52,670 --> 00:07:55,909
So the late Princess Xin and I share
the bond of being fellow disciples.

146
00:07:55,909 --> 00:07:57,280
I'm deeply honored.

147
00:07:57,550 --> 00:07:59,260
I'll definitely do everything in my power

148
00:07:59,260 --> 00:08:00,670
to bring the cause of
the late Princess's death

149
00:08:00,670 --> 00:08:01,700
to light.

150
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:04,820
Thank you, Wan.

151
00:08:45,950 --> 00:08:47,080
The skull is intact,

152
00:08:48,110 --> 00:08:49,420
muscle lines unclear,

153
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:51,620
small and thin.

154
00:08:55,310 --> 00:08:56,910
The pelvis is wide and short,

155
00:08:58,020 --> 00:08:59,350
with thin pelvic walls.

156
00:09:00,540 --> 00:09:02,540
The side walls are flat and shallow.

157
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:06,470
The pelvic cavity is short and wide,

158
00:09:06,470 --> 00:09:08,130
forming a cylindrical shape.

159
00:09:09,660 --> 00:09:11,390
The corpse is well-preserved,

160
00:09:11,780 --> 00:09:14,180
and there are obvious signs of childbirth.

161
00:09:15,350 --> 00:09:16,100
Yan.

162
00:09:17,870 --> 00:09:19,190
The late Princess was

163
00:09:19,190 --> 00:09:21,140
in the prime of her youth when she died.

164
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:23,400
Since you suspect
the cause of her death,

165
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:24,990
what unusual symptoms

166
00:09:24,990 --> 00:09:26,590
did she show before passing?

167
00:09:29,310 --> 00:09:30,230
That day,

168
00:09:30,990 --> 00:09:32,520
Mother went into the palace

169
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:36,070
to deliver medicine
she personally prepared for the Empress.

170
00:09:36,070 --> 00:09:38,930
She only returned home
after the night watch began.

171
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:41,680
As soon as she got home,

172
00:09:41,900 --> 00:09:43,700
she shut herself in her bedroom.

173
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:44,900
I was worried,

174
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:46,790
so I snuck in to check on her.

175
00:09:59,470 --> 00:10:00,260
Ze.

176
00:10:01,540 --> 00:10:02,340
Ze!

177
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:06,350
Ze...

178
00:10:06,350 --> 00:10:06,940
At first,

179
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,470
Mother only had chest pains.

180
00:10:08,470 --> 00:10:09,230
Ze!

181
00:10:09,230 --> 00:10:10,870
Then she lost her sight.

182
00:10:11,190 --> 00:10:12,310
Soon after, her hearing

183
00:10:12,310 --> 00:10:13,190
failed as well.

184
00:10:14,070 --> 00:10:15,620
Before dying, she lost all her senses

185
00:10:15,620 --> 00:10:17,750
and was vomiting blood continuously.

186
00:10:17,830 --> 00:10:18,950
In just one night,

187
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,670
she was gone.

188
00:10:21,140 --> 00:10:22,800
The imperial physician came,

189
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:24,470
but claimed that Mother

190
00:10:24,660 --> 00:10:26,320
showed no signs of poisoning.

191
00:10:26,590 --> 00:10:27,660
But since that day,

192
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:29,710
my health

193
00:10:30,780 --> 00:10:31,780
and my eyesight

194
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,990
have been deteriorating day by day.

195
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:37,320
Did the physician examine that cup of tea?

196
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:42,230
Since the physician said

197
00:10:42,710 --> 00:10:43,910
it wasn't poisoning,

198
00:10:45,310 --> 00:10:47,910
why would he bother with
such trivial matters?

199
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:54,620
May I perform an autopsy
and test for poison on the late Princess?

200
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,810
The color of these bones

201
00:11:21,990 --> 00:11:23,420
is too dull.

202
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:34,470
Use mine.

203
00:11:35,110 --> 00:11:35,590
No.

204
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:38,910
Mine should be used.

205
00:12:03,380 --> 00:12:05,840
The late Princess indeed
died of poisoning.

206
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:16,150
The mystery that has troubled me

207
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:19,230
for years is finally solved.

208
00:12:22,060 --> 00:12:23,030
Thank you, Wan.

209
00:12:35,190 --> 00:12:37,050
The incense is cool and delicate,

210
00:12:37,470 --> 00:12:40,930
carrying a serene grace reminiscent
of winter plum blossoms.

211
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:44,590
It's seemingly made from
submerged agarwood,

212
00:12:44,590 --> 00:12:45,310
cloves,

213
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:47,140
and rose water.

214
00:12:48,310 --> 00:12:49,110
Indeed.

215
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:51,310
This incense

216
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:53,500
is called Soul-Reviving Plum,

217
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:55,500
my late mother's favorite incense.

218
00:12:57,260 --> 00:12:58,420
If you like it, Wan,

219
00:12:59,230 --> 00:13:00,760
I'll make some more for you.

220
00:13:00,990 --> 00:13:01,710
Yan.

221
00:13:01,990 --> 00:13:03,250
You still need to avoid

222
00:13:03,260 --> 00:13:04,590
straining your eyes.

223
00:13:05,110 --> 00:13:06,910
Since childhood, my late mother

224
00:13:07,310 --> 00:13:09,780
had taught me how to craft
and appreciate incense.

225
00:13:09,780 --> 00:13:10,470
Now,

226
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:12,530
whenever I blend fragrances,

227
00:13:12,740 --> 00:13:13,920
it feels as if Mother

228
00:13:14,020 --> 00:13:15,660
is still right here by my side.

229
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:18,140
Yan, you still have your mother's memories
for comfort.

230
00:13:18,140 --> 00:13:20,200
That's already much more than I have.

231
00:13:27,310 --> 00:13:28,110
Chi.

232
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:31,390
Have you ever questioned

233
00:13:32,190 --> 00:13:33,850
your mother's cause of death?

234
00:13:35,540 --> 00:13:37,140
What do you mean by that, Yan?

235
00:13:38,070 --> 00:13:40,800
Less than seven days
after my mother passed away,

236
00:13:40,900 --> 00:13:41,830
your mother

237
00:13:42,420 --> 00:13:43,470
died due to

238
00:13:43,830 --> 00:13:45,230
postpartum hemorrhage.

239
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:47,590
In life, they were

240
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:49,380
close friends,

241
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:53,030
and they both met tragic deaths
almost simultaneously,

242
00:13:53,230 --> 00:13:54,950
which seems too coincidental.

243
00:13:54,950 --> 00:13:56,770
The Empress Dowager and my late father

244
00:13:56,770 --> 00:13:58,350
never mentioned this to me.

245
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:00,940
Back then, your father entrusted you,

246
00:14:00,940 --> 00:14:03,340
barely 100 days old,
to the Empress Dowager

247
00:14:03,660 --> 00:14:05,260
and went to Shuoxi alone.

248
00:14:05,590 --> 00:14:07,590
Rumors spread throughout the capital,

249
00:14:07,590 --> 00:14:08,900
saying that your father believed

250
00:14:08,900 --> 00:14:10,500
you weren't his biological son,

251
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:11,590
so he abandoned you

252
00:14:11,590 --> 00:14:13,590
and returned to Shuoxi in anger.

253
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:15,700
If not orchestrated,

254
00:14:16,230 --> 00:14:18,560
how could the rumors all be so consistent?

255
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:21,240
Yan Chi.

256
00:14:22,260 --> 00:14:23,740
Rumors stop with the wise.

257
00:14:24,070 --> 00:14:25,540
These petty tricks

258
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:27,410
are nothing compared to Father's

259
00:14:27,540 --> 00:14:28,740
loyalty and courage.

260
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:37,620
Yan.

261
00:14:38,900 --> 00:14:40,230
Are you suggesting that

262
00:14:41,230 --> 00:14:42,710
my mother was framed?

263
00:14:43,420 --> 00:14:44,750
I have only suspicions,

264
00:14:45,230 --> 00:14:46,260
but no proof.

265
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:48,150
With all these considered,

266
00:14:48,470 --> 00:14:50,020
Chi and Wan, please

267
00:14:50,470 --> 00:14:51,930
help me uncover the truth.

268
00:14:52,070 --> 00:14:54,820
Yan, since you've suspected the causes of
the Princesses' deaths for years,

269
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:56,410
have you discovered anything about

270
00:14:56,410 --> 00:14:58,340
the culprit's identity or motive?

271
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:02,240
Since my father followed my mother
in death,

272
00:15:02,620 --> 00:15:03,470
I, as a

273
00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:06,260
blind and frail royal descendant,

274
00:15:07,020 --> 00:15:09,420
despite all my suspicions and resentment,

275
00:15:10,540 --> 00:15:11,740
am powerless.

276
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:18,190
Chi, if you and Wan

277
00:15:18,990 --> 00:15:21,190
can help resolve my doubts,

278
00:15:21,740 --> 00:15:22,600
I would be

279
00:15:22,900 --> 00:15:23,900
deeply grateful.

280
00:15:32,230 --> 00:15:33,020
Yan Chi.

281
00:15:33,350 --> 00:15:35,350
Childbirth for a woman
is like passing through death's door.

282
00:15:35,350 --> 00:15:36,420
Even without poison,

283
00:15:36,420 --> 00:15:38,720
there are many ways
that can cause death.

284
00:15:38,950 --> 00:15:40,680
Mother has been gone for years.

285
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:42,620
Even if I were to exhume her remains now,

286
00:15:42,620 --> 00:15:44,470
