the late Princess Xin,

289
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:50,470
so as not to disturb Mother's spirit.

290
00:15:51,660 --> 00:15:54,230
Do you know who the late Princess Xin

291
00:15:54,380 --> 00:15:56,310
brought medicine to in the palace?

292
00:15:57,540 --> 00:15:58,600
It was His Majesty.

293
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:01,620
