back then.

294
00:16:01,620 --> 00:16:04,020
If the late Princess Xin
hadn't brought medicine into the palace,

295
00:16:04,020 --> 00:16:05,660
he might not have survived.

296
00:16:06,660 --> 00:16:07,470
So you mean

297
00:16:08,260 --> 00:16:09,990
the person who poisoned Mother

