00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:32,470
But that doesn't make sense either.

310
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:34,420
Why target the late Princess Xin?

311
00:16:36,620 --> 00:16:37,220
Forget it.

312
00:16:37,710 --> 00:16:38,950
There are too few clues.

313
00:16:38,950 --> 00:16:40,610
I'm at a loss at how to proceed.

314
00:16:40,830 --> 00:16:41,870
Too many things

315
00:16:42,420 --> 00:16:44,020
are connected to the palace.

316
00:16:44,310 --> 00:16:46,770
Let's investigate Prince Jin's case first.

