very different from usual,

320
00:16:53,910 --> 00:16:55,500
as if he remembered something

321
00:16:55,500 --> 00:16:57,070
but was afraid to speak of it.

322
00:16:57,070 --> 00:16:58,310
In the next few days,
I want to enter the palace more often

323
00:16:58,310 --> 00:17:00,740
to keep the Empress Dowager
and Sui company.

324
00:17:00,740 --> 00:17:01,990
With everything that's happened,

325
00:17:01,990 --> 00:17:03,790
they must be suffering the most.

326
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:11,230
There's one more thing.

327
00:17:13,030 --> 00:17:14,790
Jiang Heying,
the one who assassinated Father,

328
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:16,270
indeed works for Yan Qi.

329
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:17,980
Yan Qi has been sending him money
frequently these years

330
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:19,380
to train assassins.

331
00:17:19,790 --> 00:17:20,720
When His Majesty

332
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:23,619
allowed him to return to his hometown
in Qianzhou as a chief general,

333
00:17:23,619 --> 00:17:26,660
