00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:33,790
In the royal family,
there are no true father-son bonds,

338
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:36,190
let alone uncle and nephew relationships.

339
00:17:36,460 --> 00:17:37,140
However,

340
00:17:37,700 --> 00:17:39,620
whether Prince Cheng acted on his own

341
00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:40,830
or under His Majesty's orders,

342
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:41,900
