00:17:48,220 --> 00:17:49,510
We need to find a way

346
00:17:49,980 --> 00:17:52,380
to make Yan Qi
fall out of royal favor first.

347
00:17:52,420 --> 00:17:53,750
Don't worry about that.

348
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:55,180
I already have a plan.

349
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:57,220
Now that he has hopes of becoming heir,

