to the Imperial Clan Court
for investigation immediatelyâ€”

506
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:52,620
be sure

507
00:25:52,620 --> 00:25:54,950
to find the mastermind behind this arson.

508
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:56,940
As for

509
00:25:58,220 --> 00:26:00,030
the search for Che,

510
00:26:02,390 --> 00:26:03,920
leave that to Prince Cheng.

511
00:26:07,650 --> 00:26:08,300
As

512
